title: Ravens, Dak Prescott, Kirk Cousins, Cam Newton, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Ravens, Dak Prescott, Kirk Cousins, Cam Newton, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses why people shouldn't overreact over the Baltimore Ravens loss to the Cincinnati Bengals, why Dallas Cowboys QB Dak Prescott is average, what to expect from Minnesota Vikings QB Kirk Cousins, why Carolina Panthers QB Cam Newton is playing in the wrong era, and his Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include T. J. Houshmandzadeh, Eric Dickerson, and Petros Papadakis.
